Sentencas: To both increase the power density of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) and maintain its beneficial feature of secure sealing, a flat-tube high power density (HPD) solid oxide fuel cell is under development by Siemens Westinghouse, based on their formerly developed tubular model.
Titulo: Numerical simulation of heat transfer and fluid flow of a flat-tube high power density solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In this paper, a three dimensional numerical model to simulate the steady state heat transfer and fluid flow of a flat-tube HPD-SOFC is developed.
Titulo: Numerical simulation of heat transfer and fluid flow of a flat-tube high power density solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A computer code is Programmed using the FORTRAN language to solve the governing equations for continuity, momentum, and energy conservation.
Titulo: Numerical simulation of heat transfer and fluid flow of a flat-tube high power density solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The highly coupled temperature and flow fields of the air stream and the fuel stream inside and outside a typical channel of a one-rib flat-tube HPD-SOFC are investigated.
Titulo: Numerical simulation of heat transfer and fluid flow of a flat-tube high power density solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This heat transfer and fluid flow results will be used to simulate the overall performance of a flat-tube HPD-SOFC in the near future, and to help optimize the design and operation of a SOFC stack in practical applications.
Titulo: Numerical simulation of heat transfer and fluid flow of a flat-tube high power density solid oxide fuel cell
